Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.59,0:01:34.18,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yuzu...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.85,0:01:39.72,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You're noisy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.02,0:01:42.98,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I guess one hostage is enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.12,0:01:56.57,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Karin!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.66,0:01:59.29,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.70,0:02:01.45,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I still have a hostage.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.79,0:02:03.71,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I've been waiting for you, Shinigami.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.04,0:02:05.71,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Karin!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.25,0:02:08.21,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Ichi-nii...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.05,0:02:16.72,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.02,0:02:29.32,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What's... going on...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.15,0:02:35.95,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard... You're the one who was\non the bank that day, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.87,0:02:37.66,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Six years ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.12,0:02:39.41,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.33,0:02:40.95,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Six years ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.95,0:02:42.75,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo, you don't mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.33,0:02:43.71,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.29,0:02:46.71,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That day, I tried to save this kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.21,0:02:49.71,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But... when I woke up, he had disappeared...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.88,0:02:51.46,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...and my mom was...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.59,0:02:54.34,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...my mom was...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.51,0:02:57.22,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Six years ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.72,0:03:00.68,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I don't remember anything that long ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.43,0:03:03.85,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I see, this is interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.49,0:03:18.62,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The Ground Fisher...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.37,0:03:20.12,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's its codename.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.16,0:03:22.62,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It hides itself...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.16,0:03:25.71,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...and makes the appendage growing\nout of its head take human form.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.54,0:03:27.87,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Then any human who can see it...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.79,0:03:32.05,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...in other words, any human with\na soul of high spirit density...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.55,0:03:34.42,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...becomes fodder to increase its power.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.34,0:03:40.30,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That Hollow has evaded us Shinigami for over 50 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.01,0:03:43.72,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,And its favorite meal is...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.85,0:03:45.35,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...women.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.23,0:03:46.85,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Which means...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.73,0:03:48.85,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...this thing killed my mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.82,0:03:57.20,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.70,0:04:03.03,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You're a lucky kid to have survived after seeing me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.70,0:04:08.33,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,At first, I may have been trying to eat you\nbecause of your great spirit power.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.96,0:04:13.88,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But women just look so tasty.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.51,0:04:17.22,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.01,0:04:20.76,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,There aren't many Hollows that piss me off as much as this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.44,0:04:30.40,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Karin!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.57,0:04:36.74,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be careless, you fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.66,0:04:47.12,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.21,0:04:53.42,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You're the only one I'll NEVER forgive!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.01,0:04:59.47,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Disintegrate, Black Dog of Rondanini!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.05,0:05:03.55,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Look upon yourself and burn; tear away your own throat!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.60,0:05:05.39,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Way of Binding, Number 9...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.01,0:05:06.35,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,GEKI!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.81,0:05:15.15,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Don't disturb me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.91,0:05:29.29,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, I'm going to eat this girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.41,0:05:30.54,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What are you going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.25,0:05:32.00,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Karin!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.30,0:05:37.30,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,STOP!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.46,0:05:41.72,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,So, you'll be good and let me eat you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.99,0:06:00.69,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Karin!!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.55,0:06:23.93,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.76,0:06:25.22,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.14,0:06:30.64,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you do that...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.18,0:06:36.35,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Shinigamis keep fighting the Hollows, no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.15,0:06:42.32,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Shinigamis never forgive Hollows.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.32,0:06:46.82,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Because of Hollows attacking indiscriminately...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.66,0:06:49.16,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...precious people are lost...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.79,0:06:51.83,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...and only emptiness is left.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.04,0:06:54.79,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I won't forgive that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.33,0:06:59.09,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Protect them, spiky boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.67,0:07:01.67,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You understand, don't you...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.17,0:07:02.51,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.13,0:07:08.01,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me he died even though he's a Shinigami.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.14,0:07:12.10,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Even Shinigamis are not immortal.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.98,0:07:14.43,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The form may be different, but death is-
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.82,0:07:22.23,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, that bastard's sleeping...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.32,0:07:24.07,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.82,0:07:25.49,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's confusing!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.49,0:07:26.99,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Nee-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.82,0:07:30.91,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,W-Whoa, this is getting jacked up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.79,0:07:32.08,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Kon!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.49,0:07:34.12,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Take the sisters and run away!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.33,0:07:37.96,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What about you, Nee-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.29,0:07:38.75,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.17,0:07:39.54,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.59,0:07:46.63,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo, back me up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.68,0:07:48.13,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.26,0:07:52.01,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Rukia, stay back.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.43,0:07:53.01,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.81,0:07:56.14,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This time, you mind your own business.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.64,0:07:59.06,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do this alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.48,0:08:00.31,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.65,0:08:01.40,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That thing is strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.94,0:08:02.36,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I told you...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.82,0:08:05.28,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It has avoided the Shinigamis for over 50 yea-
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.32,0:08:05.74,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.28,0:08:08.70,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.62,0:08:11.91,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Don't interfere.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.95,0:08:13.45,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.54,0:08:16.58,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...MY fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.81,0:08:34.89,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... Karin...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.57,0:08:37.18,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,A-Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.02,0:08:45.44,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's exhausting to keep my brow furrowed all the time!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.03,0:08:49.28,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,How does that freakin' Ichigo keep his face like this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.70,0:08:49.99,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Geez!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.50,0:09:05.30,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Too slow, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.26,0:09:15.97,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.14,0:09:23.10,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,With your abilities, I' m surprised you had the guts\nto tell me to stay away from your friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.65,0:09:24.77,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Eh, boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.61,0:09:26.44,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.95,0:09:35.12,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,After mom died...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.62,0:09:39.29,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...I couldn't imagine how sad Yuzu felt...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.91,0:09:43.67,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...I couldn't imagine how lonely Karin felt...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.25,0:09:47.05,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Protect them, spiky boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.13,0:09:52.55,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I decided I would protect them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.26,0:09:57.26,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.10,0:10:00.10,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...beat this bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.61,0:10:07.98,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't your friend tell you not to be careless?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.32,0:10:17.58,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,How many times now have you lunged\nat your enemy without a plan?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.33,0:10:23.87,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's the definition of "careless", boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.90,0:10:51.65,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Impulsive...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.94,0:10:53.03,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You're impulsive!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.78,0:10:56.28,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You sent away your comrade based on a fleeting emotion...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.57,0:10:59.49,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...and on a fleeting emotion, you lunge at your enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.99,0:11:03.66,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,And in this way, you will perform for\nmy amusement and die at the end!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.67,0:11:06.17,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.17,0:11:06.71,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Stay away.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.46,0:11:09.63,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Keep away, Rukia!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.30,0:11:11.25,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to beat him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.92,0:11:13.05,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Even if my arm gets severed...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.38,0:11:14.34,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Even if my leg gets tossed...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.01,0:11:16.13,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'll beat him!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.51,0:11:19.18,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That is why you will die.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.97,0:11:22.89,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Because you are young, you anger easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.18,0:11:25.27,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Because you anger, your heart is in chaos.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.60,0:11:29.31,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,And because your heart is in chaos, your blade is dulled.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.86,0:11:31.40,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's over, boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.86,0:11:35.61,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You are far too young to fight with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.41,0:11:43.79,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo, is that...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.04,0:11:45.87,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You son of a bitch...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.38,0:11:55.47,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Even the most hardened of Shinigamis have\nat least one person they could never kill.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.22,0:11:57.88,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That is absolute.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.01,0:12:04.18,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,By finding that person, I have so far evaded the Shinigamis.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.68,0:12:09.77,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,And for you, that person must be this woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.02,0:12:12.61,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, isn't it Ichigo?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.99,0:12:16.53,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.45,0:12:19.41,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,And what of pride?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.16,0:12:25.00,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If you help him now, yes, you can probably save his life.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.95,0:12:26.29,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.66,0:12:30.21,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...at the same time, it will kill his pride for all eternity.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.63,0:12:31.96,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.50,0:12:33.25,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Remember this well.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.46,0:12:35.63,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,There are two kinds of fights.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.84,0:12:39.38,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We must always know the difference.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.18,0:12:42.80,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,A fight to defend life...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.22,0:12:46.02,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...and a fight to defend pride...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.52,0:12:49.06,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.15,0:12:52.86,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This is a fight for Ichigo to defend his pride...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.57,0:12:56.82,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...a fight I musn't interfere with.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.36,0:13:00.24,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Don't interfere...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.28,0:13:01.91,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Don't interfere...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.62,0:13:03.37,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Don't interfere...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.62,0:13:08.37,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Don't die, Ichigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.17,0:13:15.46,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, crap.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.30,0:13:17.13,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I fell asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.92,0:13:19.67,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Damn.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.10,0:13:27.22,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Can you raise your sword to this woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.98,0:13:29.64,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.48,0:13:32.81,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have any idea what you're doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.73,0:13:39.40,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Don't bring out... my mom's image... in a place like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.53,0:13:42.49,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Don't, Ichigo.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.24,0:13:44.24,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Put your sword away.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.41,0:13:47.24,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Don't kill mommy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.58,0:13:51.16,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.27,0:14:09.22,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I told you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.98,0:14:12.06,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Anger dulls the blade.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.10,0:14:15.77,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It will be over with the next attack, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.27,0:14:18.11,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Let me pay my respects to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.23,0:14:24.07,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Of all the Shinigamis I've encountered, you\nwere the youngest, the most impulsive...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.78,0:14:27.78,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...and by far, the WEAKEST!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.74,0:14:29.37,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.00,0:14:38.55,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.47,0:14:41.88,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Is that...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.68,0:14:46.68,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.19,0:14:58.19,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's the mother's soma.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.86,0:15:00.44,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Her wish has taken form.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.94,0:15:05.24,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Are you saying the lure remembered his mother's dying wish?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.82,0:15:08.53,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Dying wish...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.79,0:15:12.70,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I glimpsed her earlier...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.79,0:15:15.79,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This fight's still up in the air.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.96,0:15:18.54,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.13,0:15:25.01,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so proud.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.09,0:15:26.59,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.97,0:15:27.34,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...Karin...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.80,0:15:28.18,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...Yuzu...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.80,0:15:29.68,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...and you, Ichigo.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.35,0:15:35.89,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm truly proud to have known you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.98,0:15:42.57,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo, live.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.15,0:15:44.61,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Be strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.03,0:15:46.61,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Be gentle.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.82,0:15:49.82,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,And smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.29,0:15:56.33,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.68,0:16:11.22,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.93,0:16:14.47,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.77,0:16:18.65,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's what you were thinking that time?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.32,0:16:23.23,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Anger dulls the blade?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.82,0:16:26.36,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You may be right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.11,0:16:27.78,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.49,0:16:30.03,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You're wrong about one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.66,0:16:32.66,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,To beat a loser like you...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.45,0:16:36.54,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...a dull blade is more than enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.13,0:16:42.75,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If I were the rain...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.80,0:16:53.14,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...that binds together the earth and the sky,\nwho in all eternity will never mingle...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.97,0:16:57.48,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...would I be able to bind the hearts of people together?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.27,0:17:02.94,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Kurosaki-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.90,0:17:08.32,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like I can understand you a little bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.21,0:17:21.58,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.83,0:17:23.29,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I won't forgive you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.88,0:17:25.75,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Just a mere Shinigami!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.34,0:17:29.30,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Come back here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.51,0:17:33.01,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.47,0:17:35.81,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.22,0:17:36.81,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.47,0:17:39.68,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Neither you nor he can fight anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.23,0:17:41.48,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The fight is over!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.10,0:17:42.73,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.81,0:17:45.44,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,He's not dead yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.28,0:17:47.07,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I still haven't-
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.07,0:17:47.48,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.75,0:17:59.79,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You survived.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.46,0:18:00.91,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.79,0:18:02.29,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.92,0:18:05.46,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,He's one bad ass kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.92,0:18:10.05,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,A Shinigami's spirit power is the same thing as his life force.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.43,0:18:13.34,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,He could become a monster some day.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.89,0:18:18.14,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, I'm goin' home.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.73,0:18:23.06,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not crazy enough to tear apart a serious couple.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.77,0:18:26.31,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'll just tell them Rukia-chan's reached that age.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.32,0:18:26.86,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.90,0:18:30.15,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I'll just make something up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.82,0:18:32.53,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, if they find out, they find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.61,0:18:34.95,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Buh-bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.05,0:18:57.55,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.39,0:19:01.93,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't able to avenge you, Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.44,0:19:09.02,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Well, as long as you show her you're healthy,\nshe can rest assured on the other side.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.48,0:19:13.03,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Don't eavesdrop on your son talking to himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.28,0:19:16.45,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you quit.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.25,0:19:24.04,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,She complimented me on it when we first started dating.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.96,0:19:27.33,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,"Your hand looks cool when you're smoking," she said.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.17,0:19:34.67,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Thinking about it now, that was the first\nand the last time she complimented me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.55,0:19:38.47,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,So I smoke just this one day every year.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.85,0:19:39.89,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Here in front of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.47,0:19:42.81,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,How can you smile?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.31,0:19:46.35,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Why isn't anyone blaming me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.65,0:19:48.52,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This is too hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.23,0:19:51.36,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If you'd just tear into me, it'd be easier...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.11,0:19:52.69,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Why...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.32,0:19:55.03,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Why should I blame you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.07,0:20:02.29,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If I blamed you for Masaki's death, she'd get angry at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.50,0:20:06.25,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't anyone's fault that Masaki died.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.00,0:20:07.54,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's just that...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.83,0:20:13.80,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...the woman I fell in love with was a woman\nwho didn't mind dying to protect her kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.59,0:20:17.97,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,And don't forget...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.14,0:20:23.72,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...you're the man who the woman I fell\nin love with lost her life to protect.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.64,0:20:25.18,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.27,0:20:30.23,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Owww!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.77,0:20:32.32,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Live to the fullest, Ichigo.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.32,0:20:35.44,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Live to the fullest...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.53,0:20:36.57,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...age to the fullest...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.74,0:20:37.65,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...go bald to the fullest...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.61,0:20:40.12,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...and die long after I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.62,0:20:44.37,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,And if possible, die with a smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.00,0:20:47.50,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Otherwise, I won't be able to look Masaki in the eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.29,0:20:49.37,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be wishy-washy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.96,0:20:53.50,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You're still too young to look cool carrying your grief around.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.46,0:20:55.34,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be waiting down below.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.64,0:21:02.30,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You listening, Rukia?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.47,0:21:06.77,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Let me be a Shinigami for a little longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.02,0:21:09.10,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I want to get stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.02,0:21:10.68,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,More...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.88,0:21:11.44,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,More...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.81,0:21:13.57,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Stronger so I can protect them from Hollows...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.40,0:21:15.40,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...protect the people being targeted.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.44,0:21:17.44,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to beat him!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.78,0:21:19.24,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Otherwise...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.49,0:21:22.57,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I won't be able to face my mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.29,0:21:27.75,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.94,0:22:37.56,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That was a fearsome Hollow!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.98,0:22:40.40,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This time, I was pitiful, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.40,0:22:42.78,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, the man, the one Kon-sama will
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.78,0:22:44.61,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,stride over flowers and storms alike
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.61,0:22:47.28,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,and go full force for Rukia-onee-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.28,0:22:48.95,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have a line in the next episode.
